{"id": 3063, "genre": 1000, "title": "身为一个当代人，你都有哪些“知识依赖症”？", "description": "现如今“获取知识”这件事，都给我们带来了哪些谜思？（题图来自：iStock ©️ CSA-Printstock）", "record_count": 7171, "comment_count": 11, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20191118004732rPSduf6vT7E3Kjcs.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-11-17T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 6049, "title": "身为一个当代人，你都有哪些“知识依赖症”？", "content": "身为一个当代人，你都有哪些“知识依赖症”？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 349519, "content": "闲下来总想获得点什么知识，哪怕只是刷个瀑布流", "image": "img/option/option/20191117234046ALVQ5XDKJo28bBs0.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349520, "content": "读完一篇文章就会想总结出几条结论/知识点/“干货”", "image": "img/option/option/20191117234358bLB1sih3ECNvmzQM.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349521, "content": "如果一段文字没给出明确的知识点，就很难耐心读完", "image": "img/option/option/20191117234516EQb7rd2jpA0wqef1.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349522, "content": "很容易对知识付费/线上课程感兴趣（但又很难坚持", "image": "img/option/option/20191117235118JWTsxmSjdavHFeD6.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349523, "content": "喜欢看各种科普类知识，哪怕有些暂时并不会用到", "image": "img/option/option/201911172354166DHJsnmVpSj8v3qG.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349524, "content": "每次 get 到了什么今日新知，就会有莫大的成就感", "image": "img/option/option/20191118003906wO1iD0BxyFLNUb6v.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349525, "content": "喜欢囤书籍/文档之类的知识资料（虽然都是马了不看", "image": "img/option/option/20191118001221wnCFs1DzN7Kh4teG.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349526, "content": "记得住一大堆碎片知识，然而并不知道到底怎么用", "image": "img/option/option/20191118001436d1KTiM7hFkPRb3L9.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349527, "content": "这些我好像都没有", "image": "img/option/option/20191118002214T87tAjxKYgQE3rny.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}